Beyond a point, the best way of find needed information is by searching
for it. We support full searching capabilities on your site, what more, you
can even do faceted searching including one more of the following, 
tickets, wikis, reviews, projects, attachments, users, etc ...

No information associated with a searched entity is skipped. You can find
search boxes conviniently placed in several of the application pages, where,
based on the page you are viewing, the context of the search will be altered.
